🛡️ Spamora AI – Spam, Scam & Phishing Detection System

Spamora AI is a Machine Learning-powered web application designed to detect and classify spam or normal messages, emails in real time. The system analyzes SMS messages, emails, and text-based content to help users identify potentially harmful communications before interacting with them.

The project combines Natural Language Processing (NLP), TF-IDF feature extraction, and a Linear Support Vector Machine (Linear SVM) classifier to accurately distinguish between legitimate and suspicious messages. A modern and responsive Streamlit interface enables users to paste messages and receive instant predictions.

🚀 Key Features
Real-time Spam Detection
Real-time Phishing Detection
SMS Message Analysis
Email Content Analysis
Natural Language Processing (NLP) Pipeline
TF-IDF Text Vectorization
Linear SVM Classification Model
Interactive Streamlit Web Application
Mobile & Desktop Responsive Interface
Fast Prediction Response
Pickle-Based Model Persistence


